  <brief_title>The Outcome of Treatment of Traumatised Refugees With Psychotherapy and/or Antidepressants</brief_title>
  <official_title>The Outcome of Treatment of Traumatised Refugees With Trauma-Focused Cognitive Behavioural Therapy and / or Antidepressants - a Randomised Controlled Trial</official_title>
  <sponsors>
